  "detailed_description": "War Identity is a free to play high-adrenaline competitive first person shooter set in the remains of the once great urban centers of the US. Following a global pandemic and nuclear disaster, as food and water became more scarce than weapons, civilians took up arms to secure their own survival . Now, all across the shell scarred land of the nation, survivalist militias do battle with UMSC remnants for the few resources that remain. Are you a Marine fighting to preserve the union or a survivalist fighting to feed your community? What is your war identity?<br><br><strong>War Identity is free to play. Updated weekly with new features and improvements.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Connect your War Identity profile on our website to showcase your stats</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer (6v6) has the following game modes:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Team Deathmatch<br></li><li> Free for All<br></li><li> Capture the Flag<br></li><li> Last Man Standing<br></li><li> Domination<br></li><li> Gun Trial</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Zombies Co-op Game Mode</h2>Survive the waves and see if you can become #1 on the leaderboards with our zombie survival co-op game mode. New features will be added to the zombies game mode.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Some features of the game:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 35 Weapons<br></li><li> Gun Customization<br></li><li> 4 Weapon Loadout Slots<br></li><li> Experience System with 112 Levels<br></li><li> Clans<br></li><li> Ammo Care Package<br></li><li> Killstreaks<br></li><li> Token Store<br></li><li> 20 Unlockable Characters<br></li><li> 50+ Weapon Camos<br></li><li> 50+ Dances<br></li><li> Emotes<br></li><li> Daily TK Loot Boxes<br></li><li> Earned Stamina Attribute Per Character<br></li><li> Competitive Modes<br></li><li> Leaning<br></li><li> Lefty Mode<br></li><li> Battle Pass<br></li><li> Steam Friends</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Current Roadmap:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Battle Royale Mode (10% completed)<br></li><li> Inventory/Backpack (0% completed)<br></li><li> Perks for inventory (0% completed)<br></li><li> Twitch voting game bonuses  (40% completed)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "War Identity is a free to play high-adrenaline competitive first person shooter set in the remains of the once great urban centers of the US. Following a global pandemic and nuclear disaster, as food and water became more scarce than weapons, civilians took up arms to secure their own survival . Now, all across the shell scarred land of the nation, survivalist militias do battle with UMSC remnants for the few resources that remain. Are you a Marine fighting to preserve the union or a survivalist fighting to feed your community? What is your war identity?<br><br><strong>War Identity is free to play. Updated weekly with new features and improvements.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Connect your War Identity profile on our website to showcase your stats</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer (6v6) has the following game modes:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Team Deathmatch<br></li><li> Free for All<br></li><li> Capture the Flag<br></li><li> Last Man Standing<br></li><li> Domination<br></li><li> Gun Trial</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Zombies Co-op Game Mode</h2>Survive the waves and see if you can become #1 on the leaderboards with our zombie survival co-op game mode. New features will be added to the zombies game mode.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Some features of the game:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 35 Weapons<br></li><li> Gun Customization<br></li><li> 4 Weapon Loadout Slots<br></li><li> Experience System with 112 Levels<br></li><li> Clans<br></li><li> Ammo Care Package<br></li><li> Killstreaks<br></li><li> Token Store<br></li><li> 20 Unlockable Characters<br></li><li> 50+ Weapon Camos<br></li><li> 50+ Dances<br></li><li> Emotes<br></li><li> Daily TK Loot Boxes<br></li><li> Earned Stamina Attribute Per Character<br></li><li> Competitive Modes<br></li><li> Leaning<br></li><li> Lefty Mode<br></li><li> Battle Pass<br></li><li> Steam Friends</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Current Roadmap:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Battle Royale Mode (10% completed)<br></li><li> Inventory/Backpack (0% completed)<br></li><li> Perks for inventory (0% completed)<br></li><li> Twitch voting game bonuses  (40% completed)</li></ul>",
